   <text>
      <body>
         <pb n="1r" facs="lf_pDas_1663_dai_lns235ms_k1_r.jpg"/>
         <div xml:id="orig_div1" xml:lang="ara" type="invocation" rend="top centre">
            <p>هو</p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div1" corresp="#orig_div1">
            <p>He [God] is</p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="orig_div2" xml:lang="per" type="maintext">
            <p>
               <lb/>زبدة الاماثل و الاقران
               <persName ref="#purshottamDas">پرسوتمداس</persName>
                چودری و
               <persName ref="#parasRam">پرسرام</persName>
                قانونگوی پرگنه
               <placeName ref="#pgDhar">دهار</placeName>
               <lb/>را آخر انهاء آنکه عرضه داشتی که درین ولا در باب وصول مال نوشته ارسال داشته بودند
               <lb/>بمطالعه در آمد می باید که چنانچه قبولیت نوشته داده اند مال را
               <lb/>بوصول رسایند و عزر بیجا نکنند و چنان سعی نمایند که بوقت پرگنه بی باقی شود و
               <lb/>به تردد آبادانی و کشتکار زراعت اینده بکوشد در این باب نهایت تاکید دانند
               <lb/>تحریر فی التاریخ
               <date calendar="#hijri-qamri">
                  <num>۱۳</num>
                   شهر ذی قعده سنه
                  <num>۱۰۷۳</num>
                   هجری</date>
               <unclear>ما و</unclear>
               <g ref="#baiz">بیض</g><note>The ink and style of this baiz suggest it was written by the same person as the
                  endorsement. The 'pesh' above baiz is unusual.</note>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div corresp="#orig_div2" xml:id="trans_div2">
            <p>
               <lb/>Eminent among Equals and Contemporaries,
               <persName ref="#purshottamDas">Purshottam Das</persName>
                <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_chaudhri">chaudhri</ref> and
               <persName ref="#parasRam">Paras Ram</persName>
               <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_qanungo">qanungo</ref> of <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_pargana">pargana</ref>
               <placeName ref="#pgDhar">Dhar</placeName>
               <lb/>are informed that the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_arzdasht">ʿarzdasht</ref> that they had recently written and sent in
               the matter of the collection of taxes
               <lb/>has come to our attention. It is necessary that they [i.e. <persName ref="#purshottamDas">Purshottam Das</persName> and <persName ref="#parasRam">Paras Ram</persName>] should collect taxes [according to] whatever had been written in the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_qabuliyat">qabuliyat</ref>, 
               <lb/>and they should make no inappropriate excuses.
               And make such efforts that  the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_pargana">pargana</ref> becomes without
               arrears by the designated time.
               <lb/>And make efforts in future for the organisation of the populating and cultivation [of the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_pargana">pargana</ref>].
               Know it extremely confirmed in this matter.
               <lb/>Written on the date of
               <date calendar="#hijri-qamri">13 of the month of Zi al-qaʿda of the year 1073 Hijri</date>. <gap/>
               <g ref="#baiz">Ended.</g>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="orig_div3" xml:lang="ara" type="invocation" rend="right margin">
            <p>هوُ</p>
         </div>
         <div corresp="#orig_div3" xml:id="trans_div3">
            <p>He [God] is</p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="orig_div4" xml:lang="per" type="authorisation" rend="right margin">
            <p><lb/>حسب المُسطور مُقرر دانسته
               <lb/>بعمل آورند در بی باقی و تردد آینده
               <lb/>پرگنه مُجری خود دانند الیه الیه   
               <unclear>انچه</unclear>
               نگارد
               <g ref="#baiz">بیض</g>
               <lb/><stamp type="seal"><mentioned>
                  <persName ref="#asadullah">اسد الله</persName>
                  <persName ref="#nawazishKhan">نوازس خانی</persName>
                  <date calendar="#hijri-qamri">
                     <num>۱۰۷۲</num>
                  </date>
               </mentioned></stamp>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div corresp="#orig_div4" xml:id="trans_div4">
            <p><lb/>Knowing it settled as written, 
               <lb/>put it to action. In the matter of making the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_pargana">pargana</ref>
               without arrears and future organisation of the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_pargana">pargana</ref>, 
               <lb/>you know what is to be done. As aforementioned, whatever shall be written.
               <g ref="#baiz">Ended.</g>
               <lb/><stamp type="seal">Round black ink seal<mentioned>
                  <persName ref="#asadullah">Asadullah</persName>
                 of <persName ref="#nawazishKhan">Nawazish Khan</persName>
                  <date calendar="#hijri-qamri">1072</date>
            </mentioned></stamp><note>The location and orientation of the seal suggests it accompanies the
               authorising note and by extension that the author of the note was Asadullah.</note>
            </p>
         </div>
         <pb n="1v" facs="lf_pDas_1663_dai_lns235ms_k1_v.jpg"/>
         <div xml:id="orig_div5" xml:lang="per" type="clericalNotes" rend="top right">
            <p>پروانه وکالت دستگاه میرزا جیو در جواب عرضه داشت و تاکید
               <unclear>تحصیل</unclear>
                که موجب قبولیت
               <unclear>بی باقی نمایند</unclear>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div corresp="#orig_div5" xml:id="trans_div5">
            <p><ref type="glossary" target="#gl_parvana">Parvana</ref> of the Representative of the Court <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_mirza">Mirza</ref> <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_jiu">Ji</ref> in response to the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_arzdasht">ʿarzdasht</ref> and
               confirmation [that] the collection [of taxes] that [are] required by the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_qabuliyat">qabuliyat</ref>,
               <unclear>should be made without arrears</unclear>. </p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="orig_div6" xml:lang="per" type="laterAddition" rend="top centre">
            <p><foreign>نمبر</foreign>
               <num>۲</num>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div corresp="#orig_div6" xml:id="trans_div6">
            <p>Number 2</p>
         </div>
      </body>
